title: Why Is America OBSESSED with LGBTQ Icon Jeffrey Dahmer?! | Guest: Rekieta Law
description:
Trolls have gotten popular YouTuber Nick Rekieta deplatformed, and now they want to get him DISBARRED? He joins the show to tell us more. Also, America seems obsessed with the Netflix documentary of serial killer and gay icon Jeffrey Dahmer. And good news for Alec Baldwin! He's allowed to make movies again after killing a woman. #NickRekieta #Dahmer #alecbaldwin
